s the ongoing need for\nmodels of planets in this temperature regime to consider both 3D and magnetic\neffects when interpreting high resolution transmission spectra.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Feb 2023 17:10:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 May 2023 14:33:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-07"}
