DW is not a typical Fermi surface\nnesting scenario. These results provide new insights into the underlying\nphysics of the CDW in the kagome materials and could have implications for the\ndevelopment of materials with new functionality.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Feb 2023 18:52:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-06"}
