in time $5^k n^{O(1)}$, Feedback Vertex Set can be solved in time\n$5^k n^{O(1)}$.\n  The first two algorithms are tight due to known results and the last two\nalgorithms are complemented by new tight lower bounds under SETH.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Feb 2023 20:29:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-01"}
