(Cx) on an SRF sample test system. BCS resistance trends lower than\nreference Nb, while quench fields occur at approximately 35 mT. Our results\ndemonstrate the potential of ZrNb(Cx) thin films for particle accelerator and\nother SRF applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Feb 2023 08:45:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-01"}
