ature of varying $A({\\rm Ca})$ to the\nemergence of loop structures in addition to the initial main loop, each with\nits characteristic calcium abundance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Feb 2023 15:32:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-12"}
